---
title: Cal Smart Jerk-Spiced Shrimp with Peas and Rice and Mango Salsa
description: In this Caribbean-inspired plate, the mild heat of jerk-spiced shrimp is cut with sweet mango salsa that also brings a hit of acidity to brighten up your plate!
